                <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>ito</ex></expan> Iunio <expan><abbr>T</abbr><ex>iti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Gal</abbr><ex>eria</ex></expan> Severo <lb n="3"/>Dianensi <lb n="4"/>omnibus hono<lb break="no" n="5"/>ribus in <expan><abbr>rep</abbr><ex>ublica</ex></expan> sua <lb n="6"/>functo <expan><abbr>praef</abbr><ex>ecto</ex></expan> <lb n="7"/>cohortis IIII <lb n="8"/>Dalmatarum <lb n="9"/>tribuno <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XX <lb n="10"/>Valeriae <expan><abbr>Victric</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <lb n="11"/><expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Sempronius <lb n="12"/>Enipeus amico <lb n="13"/>optimo
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 13 (Ende): palmula. Corell: T. Iunius Severus erscheint auch in Nr. 128 als Stifter.</p>
